&lt;h5&gt;app/include/user_config.h&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Contains NodeMCU developer options, but could be of use.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;...
